org.hps.analysis.MC

Class TrackTruthMatching

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.analysis.MC.TrackTruthMatching

  • public class TrackTruthMatching
extends Object
    based off of "TrackAnalysis" Driver This class matches a track to an MCParticle as well as info about each truth hit The MC Particle with the most hits on a track wins. First tie breaker is the innermost hits, second tie breaker is highest energy particle.
